Note: This project is beta. It can be used already, but is missing some smaller features.注意：这个项目是测试版。它已经可以使用，但缺少一些较小的功能。

What is Matrix?什么是矩阵？

Matrix is an open network for secure and decentralized communication. Users from every Matrix homeserver can chat with users from all other Matrix servers. You can even use bridges (also called Matrix appservices) to communicate with users outside of Matrix, like a community on Discord.Matrix 是一个用于安全和去中心化通信的开放网络。每个 Matrix 家庭服务器的用户都可以与所有其他 Matrix 服务器的用户聊天。您甚至可以使用桥接器（也称为 Matrix 应用服务）与 Matrix 外部的用户进行通信，例如 Discord 上的社区。

Why Conduit?为什么是导管？

Conduit is a lightweight open-source server implementation of the Matrix Specification with a focus on easy setup and low system requirements. That means you can make your own Conduit setup in just a few minutes.Conduit 是 Matrix 规范的轻量级开源服务器实现，着重于易于设置和低系统要求。这意味着您可以在几分钟内完成自己的 Conduit 设置。

Other server implementations try to be extremely scalable, which makes sense if the goal is to support millions of users on a single instance, but makes smaller deployments inefficient. Conduit tries to keep it simple. The future for Conduit in peer-to-peer Matrix (every client contains a server) is also bright.其他服务器实现试图具有极高的可扩展性，如果目标是在单个实例上支持数百万用户，这是有意义的，但会使较小的部署效率低下。管道试图保持简单。 Conduit 在点对点矩阵（每个客户端包含一个服务器）中的未来也很光明。
